{"tid":2333693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大疆：實體清單不具任何約束力，仍在美國全國各地銷售","createTime":"2020-12-20T15:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T17:32:21.000Z","uid":98317,"like":4,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"68fc184c72c32a189e4777f4d0edab4c7e559579","tid":2333693,"uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T15:42:24.000Z","msg":"12月18日，美國商務部以「保護美國國家安全」為由，將中國無人機廠商大疆列入所謂「實體清單」，對該公司對美進出口進行「管制」。<br />\n<br />\n對於美方的無理制裁，大疆20日回應稱，該公司將「繼續在美國銷售」，美國的客戶可以繼續購買和使用大疆的產品，相關制裁不具法律效力<br />\n<br />\n華爾街日報指，大疆擁有領先全球的無一機技術和完整供應鏈，2020年大疆佔據全球80％無人機市場份額，被廣泛應用於植保噴灑農藥，應急消防搜救，專業測繪等領域，商務部一旦強行禁止大疆，就沒民用無人機可用了"},{"pid":"1e19e79de7a99eaeed66f00f1789f9d8497d93bd","tid":2333693,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T15:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  過唔過到海關"},{"pid":"aea4329baac2625d92041cdc30d698df8d5d994d","tid":2333693,"uid":1654,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T15:48:45.000Z","msg":"咁串係咪想試下同美國無人機摙返場"},{"pid":"2a9ed63c8d56c6d6fd280f190c54a87468ffcd88","tid":2333693,"uid":8410,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T15:49:53.000Z","msg":"有Biden 撐腰， 走出嚟串嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e77ae8730c8b0a35cf7e341a754c98e04d1dd84","tid":2333693,"uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T15:51:01.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">強国: 有CHINA JOE係度, 我而家想點都得</span>"},{"pid":"2830d0025c37fc4fa8429900e9aca535dfe2df90","tid":2333693,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e77ae8730c8b0a35cf7e341a754c98e04d1dd84","tid":2333693,"uid":76310,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T15:51:01.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">強国: 有CHINA JOE係度, 我而家想點都得</span>"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T15:51:33.000Z","msg":"留名呀祖唔記得咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}